    "For an earlier detection of DR, precise separation of DR symptoms is crucial.",
    "Technically speaking, concurrent categorization of several DR tumors is difficult due to 1) the dearth of pixel-level labels and 2) the wide variety of DR tumors.",
    "They provide a brand-new Poisson-Blending Data Augmentation (PBDA) approach to create fake images that can simply be used to increase the training examples already available for tumor separation.",
